div.h1: Dual Console Output: VGA and Serial

div.p: Bit 7: Blink / Bright BG Bits 6-4: Background Color (0-7) Bit 3: Bright FG Bits 2-0: Foreground Color (0-7)
Colors: 0=Black, 1=Blue, 2=Green, 3=Cyan 4=Red, 5=Magenta, 6=Brown, 7=Light Gray 8=Dark Gray, 9=Light Blue, 10=Light Green 11=Light Cyan, 12=Light Red, 13=Light Magenta 14=Yellow, 15=White
